g.text: Small blobs combined into larger blobs, garbage removed
64-block ranges of the same file go to single Mixed Blocks range
blocks for 16 files with consecutive NodeIds go to single Mixed Blocks range
Deletion Markers are also stored in Mixed Blocks and hashed in the same way
Deletion Marker for commitId1 doesn't affect anything
Deletion Marker for commitId2 is applied to blob1 and marks part of this blob as garbage
commitId updated to the newest commitId (commitId3) for both blobs
Deletion Markers are removed after Cleanup
